Taking the men’s title with a score of 39 points was Eric Kivavi of Machakos, who won by a point from Francis Musembi and third placed Nderitu Macharia. Taking the staff prize was Ruiru Sports Club’s Peter Mukuria, who carded 34 points to win well ahead of Benson Mwangi who managed 26 points.



